<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rustico | Tecnologia e Luta de Classes</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/static/images/logo.png">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #121212;
            --surface-color: #1e1e1e;
            --text-primary: #e0e0e0;
            --text-secondary: #a0a0a0;
            --communist-red: #cc0000;
            --rust-orange: #f74c00;
            --gradient-accent: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--communist-red), var(--rust-orange));
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.6;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Tipografia de código para elementos específicos */
        .code-font {
            font-family: 'Fira Code', Consolas, monospace;
        }

        /* Cabeçalho */
        header {
            background-color: var(--surface-color);
            padding: 2rem 5%;
            border-bottom: 4px solid;
            border-image: var(--gradient-accent) 1;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }


        nav div h1 span {
            color: var(--rust-orange);
        }

        header p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Navegação */
        nav {
            background-color: #000;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav a {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--rust-orange);
        }

        /* Container Principal */
        main {
            /* max-width: 1000px; */
            margin: 4rem 2rem;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            flex: 1;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            main {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        .post-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 4rem auto;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
        }

        .post-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(238, 88, 2), rgb(255, 44, 44));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .post-meta {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        .post-cover img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }


        /* Barra Lateral */
        aside {
            background-color: var(--surface-color);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            height: fit-content;
        }

        aside h3 {
            color: var(--rust-orange);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .manifesto-box {
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .tag-cloud {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .tag {
            background-color: #333;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
        }

        .tag:hover {
            border-color: var(--communist-red);
            color: var(--rust-orange);
        }

        /* Rodapé */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: #000;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-top: 3rem;
            border-top: 2px solid var(--communist-red);
        }

        footer p {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;           
            padding: 15px 40px;
        }

        .nav-left p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .nav-right {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .post-content h1 {
            color: #f74c00;
        }
        .post-content h3 {
            color: #c53c01;
        }
                .post-content h2 {
            color: #992e00;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar code-font">
        <div class="nav-left">
            <h1 class="code-font"> <img style="vertical-align: middle;" src="/static/images/logo.png" width="60px" height="60px" alt="Logo Rustico"> Rust<span>ico</span></h1>
            <p style="color:#5c5c5c; margin-top: 4px;">Tecnologia, Código e Classe</p>
        </div>

        <div class="nav-right">
            <a href="/">&lt; Início /&gt;</a>
            <a href="/artigos">&lt; Artigos /&gt;</a>
            <a href="/sobre">&lt; Sobre o Projeto /&gt;</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>

        <article class="post-article">

            <header class="post-header">
                <h1 class="post-title">{{ article.title }}</h1>

                <div class="post-meta code-font">
                    Publicado em 
                    {{ article.created_at | date(format="%d de %B de %Y") }}
                    • Por {{ article.author }}
                </div>
            </header>

            <section style="margin-top: 10px;" class="post-content">
                {{ article.content | safe }}
            </section>

        </article>

    </main>

    <footer>
        <p class="code-font">Trabalhadores de tecnologia do mundo, uni-vos!</p>
        <p><small>&copy; 2026 Coletivo Rustico. Todo o código fonte pertence à classe trabalhadora.</small></p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>